WEBVTT

00:03:58.720 --> 00:04:02.856
I was determined not to be
excluded from the performance,

00:04:02.880 --> 00:04:05.696
so I turned to my mother

00:04:05.720 --> 00:04:08.656
and loud enough for everyone to hear

00:04:08.680 --> 00:04:12.296
said, "Mom, I don't need a tutu.

00:04:12.320 --> 00:04:14.496
I need a fourfour."

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:15.720
(Laughter)

00:04:17.760 --> 00:04:18.976
Thanks, Mom.

00:04:19.000 --> 00:04:22.536
(Applause)

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:24.976
And although I didn't
recognize it at the time,

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:28.256
claiming space for myself
in that glorious fourfour

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:33.160
was the first step towards becoming
a radical fat activist.